  "id": "RAW_f2b8014b",
  "title": "字节 Seed 团队发布循环语言模型 Ouro，在预训练阶段直接「思考」，Bengio 组参与",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2650999819&idx=2&sn=67e037a51714cc1cf2c5d4f56ba25f8d",
  "date": "2025-11-04 03:43:00",
